name: Werewolf
description:
First public LORA. Been playing around with this for a bit, it's still rough around the edges but working well enough.

Weight Range: 0.3~0.8

Model was trained on SD 1.5 at 512,512. It likes to make things nsfw, make fur black, and add extra tails, so use plenty of tags to limit those. It does struggle with hands/claws/paws a bit.

Feel free to merge it, improve it, or just break it.

Edit: Been playing around with this a bit more. Decided to retrain it, change the images, update the tags, and trained it on few models (Anything 3, redid SD1.5, AOM3). I uploaded them all at once, choose whichever one you think will fit best for you.
